import React, { RefAttributes, useRef } from 'react'; import './App.css'; import board from './image/board.png'; function App() { const objectClass = 'drop-cell object' const dropClass = `${objectClass} drop-animation`; const coinORef = useRef(null); const coin1Ref = useRef(null); function drop(ref: any ){ ref.current?.setAttribute('class', dropClass); setTimeout(() => { ref.current?.setAttribute('class', objectClass); }, 4000); } return (
drop(coinORef)} ref={coinORef}> hello world!
drop(coin1Ref)} ref={coin1Ref}> hello world!
); } export default App;
